          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill directs the Department of the Army, through the Chief of Engineers, to act as the lead agency with respect to radioactive contamination remediation at the West Lake Landfill in Bridgeton, Missouri.</p> <p>Nothing in this Act affects the site's designation as a Superfund site.</p>]]></text>
